  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1941700/extras/bf22dd4d169c4bdd2de1c66695218275.avif?t=1696249139\" width=512 height=70 /></span><br>Exterminate zombies in style with up to 4 players online or 2 players split-screen in this action packed co-op top-down shooter. Fight unique and challenging zombies with special skills as you progress through endless waves of zombies.<br><br>Reach new heights as you try to top the leaderboards and secure a global ranking.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1941700/extras/28f8d0a4e714903b576b0b5543ea48bc.avif?t=1696249139\" width=512 height=70 /></span><br>Defeat zombies to unlock new guns and melee weapons. Upgrade your weapons as you complete levels. Flamethrowers, fireworks launchers, drum shotguns, baseball bats, you name it, we got it!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1941700/extras/bd494802c49a7489268fd568e8ccddb2.avif?t=1696249139\" width=512 height=70 /></span><br>Choose from four characters that each have unique roles to play.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1941700/extras/4e0c30e3d4fb0985e96032737ff35997.avif?t=1696249139\" width=250 height=485 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE MEDIC</h2>Carries a molotov and a health pack. Here to help you back up when you fall.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1941700/extras/3e4f4b728f2cc28c8e679ff6b886478a.avif?t=1696249139\" width=250 height=485 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE ASSAULT</h2>Proficient with any gun. Carries an explosive grenade and a sentry gun. There is no defence, only offence.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1941700/extras/059529063741aafddab98a7209655f59.avif?t=1696249139\" width=250 height=485 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE RUNNER</h2>Knows how to swing a bat. Carries a teddy bear with a distracting radio and a syringe for extra adrenaline.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1941700/extras/f4448f7722413eea95801c03b6da052b.avif?t=1696249139\" width=250 height=485 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE TANK</h2>Can take quite a few hits. Carries a stun grenade and a sling full of high calibre ammo.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1941700/extras/bf22dd4d169c4bdd2de1c66695218275.avif?t=1696249139\" width=512 height=70 /></span><br>Exterminate zombies in style with up to 4 players online or 2 players split-screen in this action packed co-op top-down shooter. Fight unique and challenging zombies with special skills as you progress through endless waves of zombies.<br><br>Reach new heights as you try to top the leaderboards and secure a global ranking.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1941700/extras/28f8d0a4e714903b576b0b5543ea48bc.avif?t=1696249139\" width=512 height=70 /></span><br>Defeat zombies to unlock new guns and melee weapons. Upgrade your weapons as you complete levels. Flamethrowers, fireworks launchers, drum shotguns, baseball bats, you name it, we got it!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1941700/extras/bd494802c49a7489268fd568e8ccddb2.avif?t=1696249139\" width=512 height=70 /></span><br>Choose from four characters that each have unique roles to play.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1941700/extras/4e0c30e3d4fb0985e96032737ff35997.avif?t=1696249139\" width=250 height=485 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE MEDIC</h2>Carries a molotov and a health pack. Here to help you back up when you fall.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1941700/extras/3e4f4b728f2cc28c8e679ff6b886478a.avif?t=1696249139\" width=250 height=485 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE ASSAULT</h2>Proficient with any gun. Carries an explosive grenade and a sentry gun. There is no defence, only offence.<br><br